{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I guess, maybe going outside and playing maybe some ball or-- or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't remember any organized activities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember reading, [? because I-- ?] I mean, grown-ups maybe yes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe they did have some books or maybe they read.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But can't remember anything being done for the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I doubt it because I don't think we even had electricity there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, this was a very-- like Radom was already, you know, civilized town, a city, whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There, I think we used kerosene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a really medieval times, [INAUDIBLE] you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess there were-- there must have been Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't really remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe-- maybe my mother didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe she could go out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they did let people out for-- I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had to be Russians because, I mean, although the Russians were probably for the-- you know, for-- for the dogs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know that maybe my uncle was bringing something from the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know that when I was working at the kitchen at that time, I remember they gave me soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So maybe my father went out to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe they gave him some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the only money I think that we had was-- was that fur.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And maybe--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had all the fur with us, until-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, when we were in Ludwipol, I think we didn't have-- we didn't have it in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did-- can't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- my mother had a big hole dug out, and they put the whole trunk of the fur, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after the war when we went there, my mother wanted to, you know, to find it and take some.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
